It can't be.

65
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,860
I wasn't hit at all.

66
00:06:09,340 --> 00:06:13,540
I can do this...no more shaking...Johann...

67
00:06:28,820 --> 00:06:30,940
Damn! The smoke's in the way!

68
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:36,420
Now! I have got to get him now!

69
00:06:36,540 --> 00:06:37,440
[PANTING]

70
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,640
[COUGHING]

71
00:06:41,820 --> 00:06:43,280
[PANTING]

72
